<p>The Dawson's Creek alum was seen sitting on Vitolo's lap on the outing. Vitolo's father, Emilio Vitolo Sr., is the owner of the SoHo eatery Emilio's Ballato, an establishment that has been frequented by celeb regulars including Rihanna, Whoopi Goldberg, Justin Bieber and Bradley Cooper.</p>

<p>Holmes was married to Cruise, 58, between 2006 and 2012, and she'd been linked to Cruise's Collateral costar Jamie Foxx, 25, since 2013. </p>

<p>The duo, who never went public with their relationship, reportedly split last year. </p>

